ch part of the anime alongside its characters in the style of Japanese paper street theater.\nA peaceful life in the bathhouse with wolfgirls awaits.\n", "short_description": "The team behind the original series has gotten together to bring you into the world of Spice and Wolf again for a second installment of VR animation! \nAnimation has evolved from \"watching\" to \"experiencing.\"\n"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Oculus_Square.png", "id": "666948167247977", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/86610715_666948170581310_6397857849105774023_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=GkRCqx4hIGkQ7kNvgEabUPW&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA0gi6_aNtWrO5juI141gLhw-wuq5z00lmi8Cw82OKfzA&oe=6709139C"}, {"file_name": "Oculus_Logo.png", "id": "1248298442180126", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75299157_1248298445513459_4217660042221025690_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=SQrPnUtda30Q7kNvgHY6AUq&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDt2AwMD9OPuDHda40gP-g6oPAcXKvyizDmwH0TBPiw-g&oe=67092030"}, {"file_name": "Oculus_Icon_mobile.png", "id": "944988136020255", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75557066_944988142686921_2558777294337714060_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=e-xBTPMNTnMQ7kNvgFnv4QY&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBRPxU3AX9M-CWBJ16oc8Q_iKMioyicvbpnnyC1jtVgEg&oe=67091927"}, {"file_name": "Oculus_Portrait.png", "id": "821345848684633", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031359_821345852017966_7561255947146577431_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=p3CqRrQjCz0Q7kNvgHzW-sP&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDvfQDDN168EFdc-_-kSHkP9sb5YjL0bFSVecGKv8ZjzQ&oe=6708F3CE"}, {"file_name": "Oculus_Landscape.png", "id": "7796862827